mention.text: Mr. Yeltsin , for one last time
the first freely elected leader of Russia
so many of Mr. Yeltsin 's gambits over the years
a fitting legacy for a courageous but disappointingly erratic man who guided Russia through the first years of a turbulent , still unfinished journey from tyranny to democracy
an iron will and a daring vision for remaking Russia into a free-market democracy
